{"storyMeta":{"storyReviewType":"NONE","storyId":"main_3_level_main_03-08_end","storyGroup":"main_3","storySort":16,"storyDependence":"main_3_level_main_03-08_beg","storyCanShow":0,"storyCode":"3-8","storyName":"黄昏","storyPic":null,"storyInfo":"“碎骨”再次倒下，但没有人露出笑容。陈没有安慰阿米娅，只是难得吐露了一些心声。\n带着各种各样的思绪，众人踏上归途。","storyCanEnter":1,"storyTxt":"obt/main/level_main_03-08_end","avgTag":"行动后","unLockType":"STAGE_CLEAR","costItemType":"NONE","costItemId":null,"costItemCount":0,"stageCount":1,"requiredStages":[{"stageId":"main_03-08","minState":"PASS","maxState":"COMPLETE"}],"prev":14,"characters":["陈","阿米娅","W"]},"lines":[{"type":"HEADER","key":"title_test","skippable":"true","mode":"BLACK_MASK","text":"第三十关（后）","id":0},{"type":"stopmusic","id":1},{"type":"dialog","id":2},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0","block":"true","id":3},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":4},{"type":"PlayMusic","intro":"$darkness01_intro","key":"$darkness01_loop","volume":"0.8","crossfade":"1.5","delay":"0.5","id":5,"musicid":0},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","block":"true","id":6},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":7},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"阿米娅。","id":8},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"——","id":9},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"已经结束了。","id":10},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":11},{"type":"dialog","id":12},{"type":"Image","image":"bg_0_coma","fadetime":"1","screenadapt":"coverall","id":13},{"type":"Delay","time":"1.3","id":14},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"人总是会超出预期。","id":15},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"感染者更会如此。","id":16},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"力量使人疯狂，欲望使人堕落。","id":17},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"像癌症一样，一点点侵蚀着所有美好的事物。","id":18},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":19},{"type":"dialog","id":20},{"type":"Delay","time":"1","id":21},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"对你来说，这面具什么意义都没有。","id":22},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我想......","id":23},{"type":"Background","screenadapt":"coverall","image":"bg_wild_a","width":"1","height":"1","fadetime":"2","block":"false","id":24},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"如果你想留着，就留着吧。","id":25},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"总有一天，这种面具会堆满你的房间。","id":26},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"所有人都要为他们的选择承担后果。感染者与否，都没有区别。","id":27},{"type":"dialog","id":28},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1.6","block":"true","id":29},{"type":"Image","fadetime":"0","id":30},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"1.6","block":"true","id":31},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.6","id":32},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"2","id":33},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"——————","id":34,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"——抱歉......","id":35,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"陈警官......我......","id":36,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"1","id":37},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"听着，阿米娅。","id":38,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"整合运动，这些人，如果他们愿意倾听你的话语，你可以尽你所能帮助他们。","id":39,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"但如果他们拒绝听取任何声音，只想把余下的所有生命献给疯狂......不要再犹豫了。","id":40,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"dialog","id":41},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.6","id":42},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"——","id":43,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"她也并没有作恶。并且，这也不是什么罪恶的下场。","id":44,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"仅仅是因为她选择了这个结果而已。","id":45,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"没人有资格去阻止她，没有人有资格去责怪她。","id":46,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"2","id":47},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但是，我.......","id":48,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我不知道......一直以来，我都觉得我们有一种责任，去帮助应该帮助的人。","id":49,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"但是，为什么......最后会变成这样。为什么她需要去一个人承担这样的后果......","id":50,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"罗德岛所做的事情，真的是正确的吗？","id":51,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"1","id":52},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"——","id":53,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"从感染了矿石病开始，人的命运就不再是由他一个人掌握的了。","id":54,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"也许在罗德岛看来，误入歧途还是可以被拯救的——","id":55,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"但是对我而言，对近卫局而言，却并非如此。可能，在必要的时候，必须......","id":56,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"2","id":57},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":58,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我只是想去改变那种永无止境的状况......","id":59,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"哪怕是一点点，一点点——","id":60,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"可是......这一切如果最后只能变成这样的结局，那我只能......","id":61,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"1","id":62},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"阿米娅。","id":63,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......","id":64,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你动摇了？","id":65,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"2","id":66},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我......","id":67,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"我不知道......","id":68,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"感染者不是被敌意溺死，就是自己走向毁灭。","id":69,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"悲剧只会一次接一次的重演。","id":70,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"在这苦恨的循环里，除了消灭矿石病之外，还有一种方法可以让感染者重拾希望。","id":71,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......那就是，熄灭这根荆棘锁链上的仇恨。","id":72,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"1","id":73},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......阿米娅。","id":74,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"给予仁慈是需要付出足够的代价的。","id":75,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"罗德岛永远也不会变成近卫局这样，也做不到近卫局那样。","id":76,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"你们罗德岛愿意接纳多少感染者，妄想通过柔软的手法拯救多少人————那都是罗德岛才能做，或者说————","id":77,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"罗德岛才会做的事。","id":78,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"dialog","id":79},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.6","id":80},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"但是，这样的事情，我不能做。","id":81,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"近卫局————更加不能。","id":82,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"2","id":83},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":84,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"1","id":85},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......至少，除了他的同胞以外，还有你会去留下他的面具。","id":86,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......如果这样的面具，注定会堆满你的房间，那就让他堆吧。","id":87,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"记住，这是你的事，不是别人的。","id":88,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"2","id":89},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":90,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"1","id":91},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"——罗德岛的小小的“领导人”。","id":92,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"如果你已经真的做好了心理准备去背负这一切。","id":93,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"做出你的选择，承担你选择的结果。","id":94,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"2","id":95},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"......","id":96,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"谢谢你......","id":97,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"陈长官......","id":98,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1#4"},{"type":"Character","name":"char_010_chen_1","name2":"char_002_amiya_1#4","focus":"1","id":99},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"......","id":100,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"陈","text":"近卫局在清扫现场之后会进行修整，之后，我会联系那个医生的。","id":101,"figure":"char_010_chen_1"},{"type":"dialog","id":102},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":103},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":104},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":105},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1","id":106},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.6","id":107},{"type":"Character","name":"char_002_amiya_1","id":108},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"阿米娅","text":"博士，我们走吧。","id":109,"figure":"char_002_amiya_1"},{"type":"dialog","id":110},{"type":"Delay","time":"0.5","id":111},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"2","ease":"InOutCubic","block":"true","id":112},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":113},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":114},{"type":"Character","name":"char_1504_cqbw","id":115},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"啧，看来人的命运总是交织在一起。","id":116,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"1","block":"true","id":117},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"互相牵绊，互相阻挠。再好的棋手都会被一些意外将了军。","id":118,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"算了，也不差。","id":119,"figure":"char_1504_cqbw"},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":120},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"0","id":121},{"type":"Image","image":"avg_ep03","x":"0","y":"0","xScale":"1","yScale":"1","fadetime":"0","screenadapt":"coverall","id":122},{"type":"Blocker","a":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"false","id":123},{"type":"Dialogue","name":"W","text":"至少，之后的事情......还算值得期待，呵呵。","id":124},{"type":"Dialog","id":125},{"type":"delay","time":"1.5","id":126},{"type":"Blocker","a":"1","r":"0","g":"0","b":"0","fadetime":"0.6","block":"true","id":127},{"type":"Image","fadetime":"0","id":128},{"type":"Character","fadetime":"1.5","id":129},{"type":"Dialog","id":130},{"type":"Blocker","block":"true","id":131},{"type":"Image","id":132}],"characters":["陈","阿米娅","W"]}